          deep_dive: "NumPy 实现：\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef entropy(p):\n    \"\"\"p: 概率分布 array，必须归一化\"\"\"\n    p = np.asarray(p)\n    # 过滤掉 0 概率（0*log(0) = 0）\n    mask = (p > 0) & (p < 1)\n    return -np.sum(p[mask] * np.log2(p[mask]))\n\n# Bernoulli 熵曲线\nps = np.linspace(0.001, 0.999, 100)\nhs = [entropy([p, 1-p]) for p in ps]\n# 峰值在 p=0.5：H=1 bit（最不确定）\n# p=0 或 1：H=0（完全确定）"
